  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you would cast a Ninjutsu or Genjutsu while you have an Elemental Condition, you can reduce the rank of that condition by 1, converting some of its left-over energy into chakra for your jutsu. <br />Your jutsu gains the release keyword from the damage type needed to inflict the condition and increase the damage by 1 damage die. <br />You can do this once per round.</p>",
